				<td colspan="2"><span>The dragons and various dragon type mobs in the new Veeshan's Peak are on Ring of Scale faction. If you are atleast dubious to this, you can roam freely throughout the entire zone, provided you dont touch the lava, as you will get agroed by the kos to all lava basilisks that hit for 800 fast and stone stun. To get the quest rewards, you must be atleast bottom ally to Ring of Scale faction, you can tell if your faction is high enough by hailing the quest npc's and if they give you quest, your faction is high enough. There is one final quest in VP that requires MAX ally to RoS, and atleast one of the other quests requires very good CoV faction.</span></td>
