				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: VP Quest questions.<a name="68465"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Oct 29 04 12:35 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>From what I have read the ones that drop the a foreign power source are the 3 protectors of zek just inside the building that leads to the lower arena area.  This is in the rear of the building.  These are the ones without the 'a' at the beginning  of their name.
<br />

<br />
I was there about 4 hours last night trying to solo them.  Very difficult.  I would like tips on this if its possible.  I tried everything in the book.
<br />

<br />
They hit in the 300's and summon.  I got one down to 20% by charming other giants and sending them at him.  He killed 2 giants then kept summoning me so I had to fade.
<br />

<br />
The protectors can be charmed.  However, they must be constantly engaged or they regen to 100% almost instantly.  You can't mezz or charm them and heal up.  This is what makes them so hard.
<br />

<br />
I pulled 2 and charmed one.  They fought against each other well and this would have worked except that when charm wears off, they summon you and you have 2 mobs hitting for up to 350 beating down on you.
<br />

<br />
Next time I go I'm bringing a tank and a cleric.  With this it would be a piece of cake.
<br />

<br />
Dumaine
<br />
</span></td>
