				<td><img src="/skins/default/images/user_IsOffline.gif" alt="Xeona is not online. Last active: 2/7/2005 9:24:25 AM" border="0" />&nbsp;<a class="SmallBoldText" href="/User/UserProfile.aspx?UserName=Xeona">Xeona</a><br></td>
